text: He jinem ate inasanam de jhudo! Ki tuhade kola tuhade vicom hi paigabara nahim a'e jihare tuhanu meri'am a'itam suna'unde si ate tuhanu usa dina de a'una tom dara'unde si. Uha kahinage ki asim khuda apane virudha gavaha ham. Ate unham nu sasari jivana ne dhokhe vica pa rakhi'a. Ate uha apane hi virudha khuda gavahi denage ki asim inakari si
